remente", "Equipo ensamblado correctamente", "POST exitoso tras limpieza"], "enriched": true}', 'RUN', 'Media', 'Backlog', 'FTE-096', NULL, 'INC-20260322-23DB', NULL, 3.0, 0.0, '2026-03-22 11:34:34.801026+00', NULL, NULL, '[]', '2026-03-22 11:34:34.801026+00');
