lmente", "Lecciones aprendidas documentadas"], "enriched": true}', 'RUN', 'Baja', 'Backlog', 'FTE-139', NULL, 'INC-20260322-7C5D', NULL, 1.0, 0.0, '2026-03-22 12:33:46.153784+00', NULL, NULL, '[]', '2026-03-22 12:33:46.153784+00');
